<K3 id="选题库" load="on_request">
话题清单 | Topic Inventory (18 topics | priority-ranked within category)

CATEGORY_A: failure_mode_articles
  A1: id=soft_splice_blind_spot
    hook: metal lacing on conveyor splices creates detection dead zone
    mechanism: metal-detector timing gap when metal splice passes through field
    bunting_solution: non-metallic soft splice (fiberglass/plastic pins) | continuous detection
    search_terms: ["metal detector splice problem","conveyor lacing metal detector","food safety conveyor splice"]
    industry: food processing | pharma | pet food

  A2: id=mild_steel_frame_magnetization
    hook: crossbelt separator frame accidentally attracts tramp metal instead of clearing it
    mechanism: mild steel becomes permanently magnetized by proximity to separator magnet
    bunting_solution: all-stainless "Newton design" crossbelt frame | ∅accidental_magnetization
    search_terms: ["crossbelt separator frame material","stainless steel separator frame","crossbelt magnet contamination"]
    industry: grain | aggregate | recycling | mining

  A3: id=drum_feeder_tray_magnetization
    hook: vibratory feeder tray jams against magnetic drum separator
    mechanism: mild steel tray magnetized by drum field → material bridges and jams
    bunting_solution: 300-series stainless steel tray requirement | verified field fix
    search_terms: ["magnetic drum separator jam","vibratory feeder magnetic drum","drum separator bridging"]
    industry: aggregate | recycling | plastics

  A4: id=belt_snap_back_cans
    hook: cans collide and dent at discharge point of magnetic conveyor
    mechanism: abrupt field termination causes ferrous snap-back and part-to-part impact
    bunting_solution: decreasing-force take-off rails | 8-12 inch graduated field reduction
