    industry: metal stamping | automotive | appliance

CATEGORY_B: mechanism_deep_dives
  B1: id=parabolic_magnetic_circuit
    hook: crumpled stainless steel passes through standard high-intensity magnet untouched
    mechanism: standard fields compress to surface | parabolic circuit forces field lines outward | deep reach-out geometry
    bunting_solution: SSSC patented parabolic circuit | grabs large crumpled SS standard magnets miss
    search_terms: ["stainless steel separator magnet","parabolic magnetic circuit","SSSC stainless separation"]
    industry: recycling | scrap | food processing

  B2: id=decreasing_force_rail_physics
    hook: why graduated field release prevents the most common magnetic conveyor reject
    mechanism: field strength vs distance curve | abrupt cutoff = kinetic snap | 8-12 inch taper = controlled release
    bunting_solution: engineered take-off rail geometry | field mapped per product type
    search_terms: ["magnetic conveyor discharge design","take-off rail magnet","magnetic rail field profile"]
    industry: canning | stamping | general conveying

  B3: id=npb_vs_nhi_cartridge_selection
    hook: wrong cartridge choice costs contamination events or unnecessary reject rates
    mechanism: NPB=reach-out∧holding balance | NHI=maximum hold for contamination-critical environments
    bunting_solution: NPB for standard separation | NHI for food/pharma where any pass-through = recall
    search_terms: ["rare earth cartridge selection","NPB NHI magnet cartridge","magnetic grate cartridge type"]
    industry: food processing | pharma | pet food | plastics

  B4: id=tubeless_textile_detection
    hook: pneumatic fiber conveying lines cannot use standard tube-style metal detectors
    mechanism: sensing tube creates external interference gap | textile fibers create static buildup
    bunting_solution: meTRON Textile Series | world's only tubeless detector | direct pneumatic integration
    search_terms: ["pneumatic conveyor metal detection","textile fiber metal detector","tubeless metal detector"]
    industry: textile | nonwovens | fiber processing

  B5: id=uhmw_skirting_belt_edge
    hook: belt sag on crossbelt separators lets tramp metal escape between belt and magnet
    mechanism: unsupported belt edge sags under load | gap forms between belt and plate magnet
    bunting_solution: UHMW skirting | machined to support belt edge | tramp metal containment
    search_terms: ["crossbelt separator belt sag","tramp metal escape conveyor belt","UHMW belt skirt magnet"]
    industry: mining | aggregate | grain | recycling

  B6: id=magnetic_rotary_switch_power_outage
    hook: electromagnetic sheet handler drops load during power outage
    mechanism: electromagnets release on power loss | permanent magnets hold indefinitely without power
    bunting_solution: pneumatic rectangular rotary actuator + permanent magnet + flex coupler = hold on power loss
    search_terms: ["magnetic sheet handler power outage","permanent magnet sheet fanner","electromagnetic vs permanent magnet safety"]
    industry: steel service centers | metal fabrication | automotive stamping

CATEGORY_C: selection_guides
  C1: id=belt_tension_selection_guide
    hook: over-tensioned belts are the most common cause of premature magnetic conveyor failure
    mechanism: tension∝motor load∧belt wear | minimum tension = belt doesn't slip on drive pulley
    bunting_solution: run as loose as possible | bareback (low-friction) backing for high-load | belt life math
    variables: load weight | drive pulley diameter | incline angle | speed | material type
    search_terms: ["magnetic conveyor belt tension","conveyor belt tension guide","belt life magnetic conveyor"]
    industry: general conveying

  C2: id=incline_angle_magnetic_strength
    hook: equipment specified for flat conveying fails on even a 10-degree incline
    mechanism: gravity component vs magnetic holding force | tall parts = higher tip moment
    bunting_solution: incline flattening rules | 2:1 height-to-diameter ratio threshold | extra strength spec
    variables: incline angle | part geometry | part weight | belt speed
    search_terms: ["magnetic conveyor incline angle","inclined magnetic conveyor strength","conveyor incline part stability"]
    industry: stamping | canning | food packaging

  C3: id=pulley_vs_curve_speed_threshold
    hook: corner curve sections cause belt heat and stretching at production line speeds
    mechanism: friction×speed×belt_length = heat buildup → stretch → tracking failure
    bunting_solution: magnetic corner pulleys @speed>120-150fpm | curves=slower_speeds only
    variables: belt speed (fpm) | turn radius | belt width | load
    search_terms: ["magnetic conveyor corner pulley vs curve","belt speed corner turn magnetic","conveyor curve heat problem"]
    industry: general conveying | food | stamping

  C4: id=nail_fastener_belt_width_rule
    hook: long fasteners on magnetic conveyor tear housing when they hang over belt edge
    mechanism: part length > magnetic rail width → part end flips off edge → housing puncture
    bunting_solution: belt width ≥ (max_part_length × 2) + rail_width | verified geometry rule
    variables: max part length | rail width | belt width
    search_terms: ["magnetic conveyor nail screw sizing","fastener conveyor belt width","sharp parts magnetic conveyor"]
    industry: hardware | fastener | construction materials

  C5: id=dairy_3a_liquid_trap_selection
    hook: standard magnetic liquid traps fail 3-A certification and trigger recall risk in dairy
    mechanism: standard gaskets ≠ sanitary | 3-A requires specific elastomers | FDA separate standard
    bunting_solution: Bunting Magnetic Liquid Traps | 3-A and FDA certified gasketing | full documentation available
    variables: fluid type | process temp | CIP compatibility | regulatory jurisdiction
    search_terms: ["dairy 3-A magnetic liquid trap","FDA magnetic separator liquid","sanitary magnetic trap certification"]
    industry: dairy | beverage | pharma | food processing

CATEGORY_D: installation_ops_tips
