    bunting_solution: Dense Wall cartridge design | outlasts thin-wall under rigorous vibration
    variables: ambient vibration level | cleanout frequency | field environment
    search_terms: ["magnetic grate cartridge durability","thin wall magnet cartridge failure","Dense Wall magnetic cartridge"]
    industry: food processing | mining | aggregate

  D3: id=no_spill_slide_gate_ops
    hook: standard slide gate designs spray product onto operator when magnet drawer is pulled
    mechanism: gate opens before product flow stops → product follows magnet out → contamination + OSHA event
    bunting_solution: No-Spill Slide Gate | positively shuts product flow before drawer moves | patented
    variables: product type | flow rate | maintenance frequency
    search_terms: ["drawer magnet slide gate safety","magnet drawer cleaning contamination","No-Spill drawer magnet"]
    industry: food processing | pharma | pet food | plastics

  D4: id=switchable_fanner_restocking
    hook: restocking heavy steel sheet stacks onto magnetic fanner is a two-person safety hazard
